{"tid":580092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政協倡去掉殖民符號　從港道路名開始","createTime":"2018-03-04T07:48:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T10:11:55.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"1c02a793e2afe031e0a169cca5742f10c6acd356","tid":580092,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:48:30.000Z","msg":"【全國兩會】政協倡去掉殖民符號　從港道路名開始　激發幼兒愛國情懷 <br />\n<br />\n全國政協小組會議在北京舉行。政協委員佘德聰建議中央政府，促使特區政府去掉和減少殖民政府留下的符號，例如由香港地名和道路名開始。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，港人回歸後都是國民，無論「一國一制」還是「一國兩制」，「愛國」是基本義務，認為香港應關注幼兒愛國情感教育，從小培養和激發幼兒愛國情懷。<br />\n<br />\n政協委員王貴國則指，不少青少年及群體不太了解內地，各界推動相關工作時，要針對青少年特點，如推廣中國傳統文化時，結合當代文化。"},{"pid":"1fc7847eb53ca9696c18021d875a3975e44a69af","tid":580092,"uid":47359,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:51:07.000Z","msg":"ok習近平伉儷紀念殮房"},{"pid":"40c23e759f4eb96664460c3502eaf01ca3cd8afc","tid":580092,"uid":57376,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:51:37.000Z","msg":"解放路<br />\n建設大道<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35fc1a4cc1a91ef3ce39abf92e5c39d51cdb8330","tid":580092,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6caaa208a03f311bde3ad425f1e44855d8f356f","tid":580092,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:52:40.000Z","msg":"我記得我fb見到不知幾撚多台狗仲嫌麻煩....嫌咩?嫌去中國化,撇清蔣中正遺毒麻撚煩不如專心拼經濟wo<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中共呢招咪好波,照搬台狗個套,一樣搞到人咁反感,但係意義完全唔撚同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26920b2358f384a0baba6457a9cfece6f1da1c0","tid":580092,"uid":68215,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:53:09.000Z","msg":"我睇唔到改街名同愛國有咩關係"},{"pid":"91a12e97a11f9aa61daf6fafdc62610d3479efbe","tid":580092,"uid":3775,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事在必行"},{"pid":"ac391c6cfcde78e5b8707da26789c9dd41b61206","tid":580092,"uid":68215,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:54:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我睇唔到改街名同愛國有咩關係</blockquote><br />\nBtw幾時將康莊道改名叫解放路<br />\n塞到仆街"},{"pid":"126c53be95a30cab5459eacbdc977507304d4605","tid":580092,"uid":42580,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:54:55.000Z","msg":"皇后大道中 - 建設大道中"},{"pid":"89bd7c5bb2dce0a3efb1992cdf45283f5a3367eb","tid":580092,"uid":74058,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:55:11.000Z","msg":"唔會有人反對"},{"pid":"681f9bee935ee753beeef336c7c94ae8d7fc8d69","tid":580092,"uid":74058,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:55:49.000Z","msg":"香港人唔會反對"},{"pid":"f621e50cf3eea782d02c50d4d31f8c8d8064acfe","tid":580092,"uid":54593,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:56:01.000Z","msg":"接受唔到"},{"pid":"f2736be329918638993c9d68bb0c9caf7cf8ebfa","tid":580092,"uid":61257,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T07:59:03.000Z","msg":"死共狗"},{"pid":"a28f0694fb6833535bd9c152cb894b02eebf0bd